<HEADLINE>
<P>
PEOPLE: CALIFORNIA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Equitec Financial Group Inc. in Oakland named Richard Saalfeld as chief 
executive. Saalfeld, who continues as president and a member of the board, 
joined the company last year. 
</P>
