JAMES A III; BUSH, GEORGE; GORBACHEV, MIKHAIL S; USSR -- FOREIGN POLICY; UNITED 
STATES -- FOREIGN POLICY; MIDDLE EAST PEACE; CENTRAL AMERICAN PEACE 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
