BOOKS; ROYALTIES; INVESTMENTS; OIL INDUSTRY -- TEXAS; JAFFE, M D JR (DOUG); 
JAFFE, M D SR (MORRIS); POLITICAL CORRUPTION; UNITED STATES -- GOVERNMENT 
OFFICIALS -- FINANCES 
</P>
