child-care center for 106 children. The tower is the first of four towers 
planned, in addition to a Hilton Hotel. Michael J. Choppin, president and 
chairman of the board of IDM, noted at the ceremonies that the combined ports 
of Long Beach and Los Angeles handle about two-thirds of the West Coast's cargo 
