</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY -- ELECTIONS -- 1989; PROPERTY TAX -- ORANGE COUNTY; ORANGE 
COUNTY -- SCHOOLS -- FINANCES; POLITICAL CONTRIBUTIONS; POLITICAL ACTIVISM; 
CAPISTRANO UNIFIED SCHOOL DISTRICT 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA051189-0171 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 55711 </DOCID>
